{
  "stem": "13851.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 494.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was some working on the mountains-- for something about planes, or planes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were terrible, in terrible condition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I didn't see no crematoriums there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were there-- as I told you, there we starting getting more often bombardment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on one night we went-- it was a bombardment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the SS run out too, out of the camps, out in the roads, because they were afraid they were gonna-- and then what happened, the bombardment quiet down.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So where would we go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no place to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went back to the-- to the camp, because we had uniforms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where you gonna go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can't go no place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that night, they took a lot of people out to be killed, because they know that's the end of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't want to-- and I-- and we were not-- we were not taken out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw them marching away, a lot of other-- the separate grouping taken out to be killed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took out a few hundred at that time, you know, just to be killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what we saw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We know the way they killing around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then, the next morning, it start to come bombardment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was 10 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was-- and I-- and went out, again-- out the camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was outside, I would say a-- maybe, a 1/4 of a mile away from the camp, laying on the ground.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And next to me was an SS laying right next to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said in German, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That means, it's-- we finished-- that's what-- in German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I felt good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't care for him to live or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I saw him next to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was even with me-- SS-- laying with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
